###

@token = {{login.response.body.$.token}}

### Listar todos as companias.
GET http://localhost:3000/company HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json


### busca apens uma compania
GET http://localhost:3000/company/2 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### BUSCAR POR NOME

GET http://localhost:3000/company?name=abrobrinha HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### BUSCAR POR TYPE

GET http://localhost:3000/company?type=bo HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### ATUALIZANDO HAHA

PUT http://localhost:3000/company/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name":     "abracadabra",
  "category": "balas",
  "cnpj":     "1234520199",
  "places":   "adacy",
  "zip_code": "1356899",
  "addrres":  "rua 2",
  "phone":    "190",
  "userId":   2
}


### Atualizar company
PUT {{baseUrl}}/company/1 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name":     "teste",
  "category": "Alimentação",
  "cnpj":     "12345678000199",
  "places":   "Localização da empresa",
  "zip_code": "12345-678",
  "addrres":  "Rua Exemplo, 123",
  "phone":    "(11) 1234-5678"
}


### Deletar company
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/company/1 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# =============================================
# Rotas públicas (sem token)
# =============================================

### Listar todas as companies
GET {{baseUrl}}/company HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json


### Buscar uma company por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/company/2 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json


### Buscar por nome
GET {{baseUrl}}/company?name=abrobrinha HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json


### Buscar por tipo
GET {{baseUrl}}/company?type=bo HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
